@type: comparison

@compare:
  header: Channel | Share of Top-Performer DTC Revenue | CAC | LTV:CAC Ratio
  row: Owned digital (website + app) | 45% | $32 | 8.2×
  row: Social commerce (IG, TikTok Shop) | 27% | $18 | 5.4×
  row: Subscription and loyalty programs | 13% | $0 (existing customer) | 12.1×
  row: Marketplaces (Amazon, etc.) | 15% | $22 | 3.8×

@exhibit: Exhibit 2 — DTC Channel Economics Benchmark
@source: BCG DTC Consumer Benchmark, 2024

@notes: Subscription programs have near-infinite LTV:CAC because they convert existing customers. Under-investment in subscription is the most common missed value opportunity in DTC.

